<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT32">
<l>kataipporuḷtāṉ kaṇṇaṉ tiruvayiṟṟi ṉuḷḷa</l>
<l>vutaippaḷavu pōtupōk kiṉṟi vataipporuḷtāṉ</l>
<l>vāynta kuṇattup paṭāta taṭaimiṉō</l>
<l>vāynta kuṇattā ṉaṭi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Stories [and] meanings are in the sacred mind of Kṛṣṇa.</l>
<l>Not getting caught in [His] surpassing qualities</l>
<l>—without spending time [otherwise] [even] for a moment—</l>
<l rend="indent">	is indeed a matter of distress!</l>
<l>Reach the feet of Him with excellent qualities.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
